# Event Flyer Webpage

## Overview

This project is a responsive Event Flyer webpage created using HTML5 and CSS3. The webpage is designed to present event information in a clean, modern, and visually appealing format while practicing important front-end development concepts.

The project includes a hero section, styled headings, event details, custom list styling, responsive images, and decorative UI elements inspired by modern web design aesthetics.

---

## Features

* Responsive webpage layout
* Styled event hero section
* Rounded image borders
* Custom typography and color palette
* Centered content layout
* Styled unordered lists with custom markers
* Decorative sections and spacing
* Hover effects for interactive elements
* Modern card-style design

---

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3

---

## Concepts Practiced

### HTML Concepts

* Semantic structure
* Sections and headings
* Images and figure captions
* Lists and list items
* Anchor elements
* Page layout organization

### CSS Concepts

* Width and height control
* Margin and padding
* Background colors
* Border and border-radius styling
* Flexbox alignment
* Hover effects using pseudo-classes
* Responsive image sizing
* List marker customization
* `calc()` usage
* `inline-block` behavior
* Text alignment and spacing

