## Design Goals

The webpage was designed with:

* Soft, eye-friendly colors
* Clean spacing and layout hierarchy
* Simple and readable typography
* Modern event flyer aesthetics
* Responsive content presentation

---

## Learning Outcome

This project helped improve understanding of:

* CSS box model
* Layout alignment
* Flexbox behavior
* Responsive sizing
* Difference between margin and padding
* Width and content sizing
* Custom list styling techniques
* UI styling best practices

